data.description: Welcome to Your Dream Home in Lancaster, CA - Enhanced with a Tile Roof and Sunrun Solar Panels!This exquisite property in Lancaster, CA 93535, now boasts a top-quality tile roof, offering both elegance and practicality. Perfectly situated on a corner lot, it provides easy access to essential amenities while offering a peaceful living environment.Key Features:Prime Location: Within a 1.5-mile radius, find grocery stores, restaurants, banks, as well as elementary, middle, and East Side High School.Elegant Tile Roof: The tile roof not only adds charm but also brings several advantages:Durability: Known for longevity, the tile roof can withstand severe weather.Energy Efficiency: Helps maintain a comfortable climate indoors, reducing heating and cooling expenses.Low Maintenance: Tile roofs require little upkeep for a worry-free lifestyle.Fire Resistance: Offers increased safety due to its fireproof nature.Interior Elegance: The home features tile floors in the living room, kitchen, hallway, and bathrooms, all under high ceilings. The kitchen is equipped with a breakfast bar, white tile countertops, and modern gray cabinets. Laminate flooring in the dining room and bedrooms adds a contemporary feel.Master Bedroom: A retreat with two large closets, high ceilings, and an en-suite bathroom with a walk-in shower.Outdoor Space: The large backyard includes a sizeable patio cover, perfect for outdoor activities, and is enclosed with privacy walls on two sides.Eco-Friendly Sunrun Solar Panels: Enjoy significantly reduced electric bills thanks to the efficient Sunrun solar panels, a smart and sustainable energy solution.Additional Rooms: The garage conversion offers two extra bedrooms, making a total of five bedrooms and two bathrooms in the home.This property offers a perfect mix of suburban tranquility and urban convenience, making it more than just a house. It's a lifestyle choice. Welcome to your dream home in Lancaster!
